extensions.description: The pigeon biggest opp of the lion

AI6900 began as a thought experiment: what happens when we train a token to observe markets, read culture, and respond like a living entity?

Every price chart becomes a dataset. Every rumor, a neural signal. Every meme, a training sample.

The result is a social-technical organism — a token that learns through the chaos of its own community. It doesn’t just follow trends; it understands them.

Because AI6900 doesn’t copy behavior — it models it.
The largest countries in the world are battling over this.
“龙图”表情包的历史，其实是一段非常典型的中文网络“草根 meme”演化史。 大约在2013年前后，一张线条粗糙、造型像“龙”的表情图片在贴吧和QQ空间悄然流行。它原本只是某个网友随手涂鸦的“丑图”，但因为那种呆滞又莫名喜感的表情，被网友大量转发、改图和二次创作。没过多久，它便形成了一个独特的“抽象梗”文化圈。
